urls.description: Using less and reusing more as part of our plan that's built to last. Today, we’re already shifting to recyclable products, sustainably sourced materials and carbon neutral operations, but our journey doesn’t end here. Learn more about our sustainability mission.
urls.title: Our plan - Sustainability | Philips

1732383982128427267.text: @McArdleNYC Thank you for your question! In 2020, we became carbon neutral in our operations (when it comes to factories, offices, our logistics and travel). More information can be found on the following page: https://t.co/cwW2sQVfvd. >>
